<template><header class="header"><a href="/" class="header__logo"><span class="header__logo-mark">M</span>Design System</a><nav class="header__nav"><a href="/" class="header__nav-link">Foundations</a><a href="/documentation/radio.html" class="header__nav-link is-active">Components</a></nav></header><div class="layout"><nav class="layout__nav"><div class="nav"><section class="nav__section"><span class="nav__section-title">Components</span><ul class="nav__list"><li class="nav__item"><a href="/documentation/button.html" class="nav__link">Button</a></li><li class="nav__item"><a href="/documentation/toggle.html" class="nav__link">Toggle</a></li><li class="nav__item"><a href="/documentation/checkbox.html" class="nav__link">Checkbox</a></li><li class="nav__item"><a href="/documentation/input.html" class="nav__link">Input</a></li><li class="nav__item"><a href="/documentation/select.html" class="nav__link">Select</a></li><li class="nav__item"><a href="/documentation/radio.html" class="nav__link is-active">Radio</a></li><li class="nav__item"><a href="/documentation/textarea.html" class="nav__link">Textarea</a></li><li class="nav__item"><a href="/documentation/tabs.html" class="nav__link">Tabs</a></li></ul></section></div></nav><main class="layout__content"><article class="content"><span class="content__eyebrow">Components</span><h1>Radio</h1><p class="content__lead">Single-selection control for mutually exclusive choices. Includes standalone radio and RadioWithLabel.</p><h2 id="purpose" class="comp-section-h2">Purpose &amp; when to use</h2><ul><li>Use in groups where exactly one option can be selected.</li><li>Use Checkbox for multiple selections.</li></ul><h2 id="anatomy" class="comp-section-h2">Anatomy &amp; sizing</h2><table class="props-table"><thead><tr><th>Property</th><th>Token</th><th>Value</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>control size</td><td>—</td><td>24x24</td></tr><tr><td>border</td><td>—</td><td>2px</td></tr><tr><td>dot size</td><td>—</td><td>12x12</td></tr><tr><td>gap with label</td><td><code>--marks-spacing-12</code></td><td>12px</td></tr></tbody></table><h2 id="variants" class="comp-section-h2">Variants &amp; all states</h2><div class="comp-demo"><div class="comp-demo__group"><span class="comp-demo__group-label">Standalone</span><div class="comp-demo__row"><Radio v-model="group" name="a" value="one" /><Radio v-model="group" name="a" value="two" /><Radio v-model="group" name="a" value="three" :disabled="true" /></div></div><div class="comp-demo__group" style="width:100%;max-width:420px;"><span class="comp-demo__group-label">With labels</span><div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:12px;"><RadioWithLabel v-model="group2" name="b" value="email" title="Email" /><RadioWithLabel v-model="group2" name="b" value="sms" title="SMS" /><RadioWithLabel v-model="group2" name="b" value="push" title="Push" :disabled="true" /></div></div></div><h2 id="behavior" class="comp-section-h2">Behavior rules</h2><ul><li>Emits <code>update:modelValue</code> with own <code>value</code> on change.</li><li>Supports standard radio grouping via shared <code>name</code>.</li><li>Disabled state prevents updates.</li></ul><h2 id="content" class="comp-section-h2">Content rules</h2><ul><li>Use short option labels and parallel wording.</li><li>Add paragraph text only when necessary.</li></ul><h2 id="accessibility" class="comp-section-h2">Accessibility</h2><ul><li>Native <code>input[type=radio]</code> semantics.</li><li>Visible focus state with primary outline.</li></ul><h2 id="examples" class="comp-section-h2">Examples &amp; anti-patterns</h2><div class="comp-demo"><div class="comp-demo__group"><span class="comp-demo__group-label">Do</span><RadioWithLabel v-model="group3" name="c" value="card" title="Credit card" /></div><div class="comp-demo__group"><span class="comp-demo__group-label" style="color:#FD3860;">Don't</span><RadioWithLabel v-model="group3" name="c" value="x" title="Option" /></div></div><h2 id="api" class="comp-section-h2">API / Props</h2><table class="props-table"><thead><tr><th>Name</th><th>Type</th><th>Default</th><th>Description</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><code>modelValue</code></td><td>String|Number|Boolean</td><td>null</td><td>Selected value.</td></tr><tr><td><code>value</code></td><td>String|Number|Boolean</td><td>required</td><td>This radio option value.</td></tr><tr><td><code>name</code></td><td>String</td><td>required</td><td>Group name.</td></tr><tr><td><code>disabled</code></td><td>Boolean</td><td>false</td><td>Disabled state.</td></tr></tbody></table><h2 id="theming" class="comp-section-h2">Theming &amp; dark mode</h2><div class="comp-demo dark-preview"><div class="comp-demo__group"><Radio v-model="theme" name="d" value="a" /><Radio v-model="theme" name="d" value="b" /></div></div></article></main><aside class="layout__aside"><div class="aside"><div class="aside__block aside__block--code"><div class="code-pane is-active"><pre><span class="token-tag">&lt;Radio</span> <span class="token-attr">v-model</span>=<span class="token-string">"choice"</span> <span class="token-attr">name</span>=<span class="token-string">"plan"</span> <span class="token-attr">value</span>=<span class="token-string">"basic"</span> <span class="token-tag">/&gt;</span></pre></div></div></div></aside></div></template>
<script>export default{name:'RadioDocPage',data(){return{group:'one',group2:'email',group3:'card',theme:'a'}}}</script>
